# ExpenseHub Pro 💰

ExpenseHub Pro is a modern expense management web application developed using HTML, CSS, JavaScript and Firebase.

## Features

- User Login & Signup
- Firebase Authentication
- Add Expenses
- Edit Expenses
- Delete Expenses
- Search Expenses
- Expense History
- Monthly Expense Report
- PDF Report Download
- Responsive Dashboard
- Firebase Hosting

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Firebase Authentication
- Firebase Firestore
- Firebase Hosting
- jsPDF

